Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:23.10,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(356,329)}Negotiation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.06,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,458)}20th December - 11:50 am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I actually came to Japan on a top secret mission, {\alpha&HFF&}so if you could refrain from mentioning to the Japanese police that... err..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I actually came to Japan on a top secret mission, so if you could refrain from mentioning to the Japanese police that... err..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone that I've met you... {\alpha&HFF&}including my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone that I've met you... including my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone to know that I've encountered the FBI either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my father were to find out, L would definitely be informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even suspect me slightly, {\alpha&HFF&}and now this incident will be dismissed as a mere accident by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even suspect me slightly, and now this incident will be dismissed as a mere accident by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? {\alpha&HFF&}What's with the big sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? What's with the big sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, {\alpha&HFF&}I was caught up in a random bus hi-jacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was caught up in a random bus hi-jacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus hi-jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A criminal, who attempted to rob a bank two days ago, {\alpha&HFF&}decided to try his luck at a bus hi-jacking this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A criminal, who attempted to rob a bank two days ago, decided to try his luck at a bus hi-jacking this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's a scary place these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just happened to be on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the culprit jumped off the bus and ended up being hit by an oncoming car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That culprit... {\alpha&HFF&}did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That culprit... did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have time to see things right through to the end though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if that wasn't just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... you were investigating someone when you got on that bus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And somehow, a criminal has ended up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, {\alpha&HFF&}I know that you were a brilliant FBI investigator, but right now, you're just my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know that you were a brilliant FBI investigator, {\alpha&HFF&}but right now, you're just my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know that you were a brilliant FBI investigator, but right now, you're just my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to remember that you're no longer an investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I won't get involved in the Kira-case."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I won't do anything dangerous."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me those things before coming here, and that's why I brought you with me, so we can visit your parents in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Ray. It's just a habit.. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Ray. It's just a habit.. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Sorry, you don't need to worry about it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we start a family, you'll be too busy to remember what it was like to be an investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have the time to slip into old habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you've got to help me think of a way to impress your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna write the name of the agent you've just identified?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. {\alpha&HFF&}It'll be a week before I'll write his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. It'll be a week before I'll write his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to die immediately after encountering me, it'd look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for me to wait till his investigation progresses further, and allow him the opportunity to investigate as many people connected to the police as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I'll bait L with some more prisoners...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}there's been another victim that's left some sort of suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, there's been another victim that's left some sort of suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send me the images.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, did you know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me that Shinigami actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, tell the police to continue surveying the prisons. {\alpha&HFF&}We may see more prisoners leaving notes behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, tell the police to continue surveying the prisons. We may see more prisoners leaving notes behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.14,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,27th December - 3:00 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's pretty busy around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where it's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally I'll be able to show you the results of the investigations and experiments I've been carrying out these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of the Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}I've been able to identify several different methods of killing people by utilizing some of the local criminals as my test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of the Death Note, I've been able to identify several different methods of killing people by utilizing some of the local criminals as my test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:58.04,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(609,170)}Accidental Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:58.04,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(444,242)}26th December              8:30 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:58.04,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(444,316)}Death from being run over by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cause of death and any further details are written in the Death Note first, and the name is added afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:58.04,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(339,162)}Hanekuroda
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person will still die exactly as it is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeh? {\alpha&HFF&}Even I hadn't realized that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeh? Even I hadn't realized that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray Penber-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around, and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you even think about turning around or putting your hands in your pockets I'll kill you instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait... This voice... I've heard it before.. somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll prove to you that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see that cafe over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a guy wearing glasses working there. I'm going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I should at least kill one person for you to take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:07:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man has a record of physically abusing women, but due to lack of evidence he's never been convicted for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only right that those who cause suffering to society should receive judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that L's told you that I'm only able to kill people if I know their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, I can kill anyone who's around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got any requests, just go ahead and ask. I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you're Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'm sure that it'd be much more painful for you to lose someone dear to you than to lose anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to consider that person as the one really being held hostage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Not her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. {\alpha&HFF&}I've done some research on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. I've done some research on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go against any of my orders, I'll kill everyone. Including your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you've brought your laptop with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have all the files of all the investigators assigned to Japan on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to work, I've always got my laptop with me, {\alpha&HFF&}but I don't have any of those files.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to work, I've always got my laptop with me, but I don't have any of those files.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please take this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, take out the transceiver and put the ear piece on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A transceiver? This is practically a toy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, this way, there'll be no record of communication, and even underground, as long as we're close enough, we'll be able to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thought this through...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, please get on the Yamanote line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:41.25,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yamanote line is a train line that circulates around central Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether you take the inside or the outside track.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be constantly observing you from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while you are on the train, look straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember that I can kill you at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've boarded, sit at a corner seat by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there isn't one free, we'll wait until there is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you several questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get an answer that completely conflicts with my expectations, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll kill your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get an answer that completely conflicts with my expectations, I'll kill your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many FBI agents have entered Japan, and how are they organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer quietly into the transceiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there are twelve of us, divided into four teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, take out the contents of the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... {\alpha&HFF&}is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to write the name of your direct superior, who should have all the names of the investigators, in the top box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? {\alpha&HFF&}What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I've got no choice but to do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he only has their names, he shouldn't be able to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'd like you to open up your laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your superior should be sending you some files soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be the files containing the names and faces of all FBI agents that have entered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like before, I want you to write each name in a box while concentrating on each of their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, what are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've finished your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please place the papers and the transceiver back into the original envelope, and leave it on the wire rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've done that, remain on the train for a further 30 minutes without moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:11:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, once you're sure that no one will notice you leaving the envelope, disembark the train at a station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... {\alpha&HFF&}why can't I remember whose voice this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... why can't I remember whose voice this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:18.86,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,4:41 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... {\alpha&HFF&}Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye... {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye... Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The papers Ray Penber wrote on, {\alpha&HFF&}were torn out pages from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The papers Ray Penber wrote on, were torn out pages from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, he killed his own teammates without even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Penber's superior died after sending the files to all members of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the investigators on the team died of a heart attack after receiving those files.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}you've got a call from the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, you've got a call from the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just heard that all our investigators that we sent to Japan have been found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them died of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that they must have been killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have to do this, L, {\alpha&HFF&}but we're going to have to cut off our investigations in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have to do this, L, but we're going to have to cut off our investigations in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Yagami is on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}I've just spoken to the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I've just spoken to the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you've been using the FBI to investigate us and those who are connected with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean to say that you actually suspected us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that it was a necessity in order to narrow down Kira's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't treat your allies as spies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't trust L after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this means that Kira must have killed FBI agents too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will kill anyone who opposes them, even if the person isn't a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is a real monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another prisoner who has left a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only eat apples
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray is..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! {\alpha&HFF&}He was killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He was killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this "family meeting" about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I tried to hide it, you'd all eventually find out, so I'll tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently heading the investigation into Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Wow, you're really amazing, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the start of my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, yesterday, {\alpha&HFF&}twelve FBI agents that were sent to Japan to investigate Kira.. all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, yesterday, twelve FBI agents that were sent to Japan to investigate Kira.. {\alpha&HFF&}all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, yesterday, twelve FBI agents that were sent to Japan to investigate Kira.. all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean they were all killed by Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to put it bluntly, {\alpha&HFF&}if I go after Kira, I may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to put it bluntly, if I go after Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}I may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to put it bluntly, if I go after Kira, I may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most horrific crime I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of my staff are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should quit as well, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Your life is far more important than your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way I'm stepping down from this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There's no way I'm stepping down from this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not bow to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's very honorable of you, father. I'm very proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything happens to you... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll make sure that Kira will be sentenced to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything happens to you... I'll make sure that Kira will be sentenced to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is willing to kill those who oppose them even if they aren't criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could all be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to think of your lives, families and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who wants to leave is free to do so. {\alpha&HFF&}There'll be no risk of demotion, I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who wants to leave is free to do so. There'll be no risk of demotion, I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those of you who have the conviction to fight Kira, even if you have to sacrifice all the things I've just mentioned, should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember him telling everyone to get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember the rest of the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? {\alpha&HFF&}I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I understand. {\alpha&HFF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my thinking is correct... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira may have been among those passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my thinking is correct... Kira may have been among those passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, {\alpha&HFF&}I should be able to use this bus as a route to get to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I should be able to use this bus as a route to get to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six people, including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}In fact, I'd like to think of it as six people willing to stand up to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. In fact, I'd like to think of it as six people willing to stand up to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to trust the six of you who have shown yourselves to have a great sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L may have just said that he trusts us, {\alpha&HFF&}but we don't trust L!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L may have just said that he trusts us, but we don't trust L!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}we've all decided to put our lives on the line to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we've all decided to put our lives on the line to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know what that means!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you've only ever given orders without revealing your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't work with someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}if you're serious about joining forces with us to catch Kira, will you come here and join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if you're serious about joining forces with us to catch Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}will you come here and join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if you're serious about joining forces with us to catch Kira, will you come here and join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said that I would trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:06.48,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like the following \Nevents to be kept secret \Nbetween the eight of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:12.46,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to meet you six, \Ntrustworthy people as \Nsoon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:21.33,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, \NI want you to leave \Nthe building and \Ndiscuss whether\Nyou choose to \Ntrust me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he asking for our support now, at the risk of exposing himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that he's solved countless cases on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be able to solve this one on his own too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, judging by his past actions, we may end up dealing with a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake, huh? Could be possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to trust L.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that L's skills will be invaluable to us in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's said from the start that this case would require the co-operation of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it conceivable that... {\alpha&HFF&}L was actually waiting for this to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it conceivable that... L was actually waiting for this to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"For this to happen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were people on the case, right from the start, who were suspicious of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People were resigning left, right and center, and information was somehow being leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been impossible for him to command the investigation with trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean L's been waiting until only those dedicated individuals he could trust, and whom are willing to stand against evil remained at headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, if you're going to join forces with L, I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't try to follow any of you, or try to find L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose to trust L and work alongside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently in a room at the Teitou hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be switching between hotels in the city every few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to request that my hotel room be used as the real headquarters during this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to these stipulations, I'd like you to split into two groups, and, leaving a gap of at least 30 minutes between the two, come up to my room before midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}right now it seems that we are moving towards each other at an even rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, right now it seems that we are moving towards each other at an even rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll expose myself as L, in front of people, for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find out about this, {\alpha&HFF&}I can guarantee that you'll try to move in on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find out about this, I can guarantee that you'll try to move in on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done quite a lot over the last few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to think hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make any mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I proceed from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real battle starts now, L!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.05,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(556,294)}To be continued
